<br>
Once you add in the addiction factor of EQ (/em points at you), VI pretty much has you over a barrel and is pokin' you from behind. Also, with new MMORPGs coming out on a monthly basis now people are looking for alternatives when VI pulls the nerf bat out of the closet. So they need to balance your addiction against the possible nerf. <br>
<br>
VI does not hire stupid people imo and it is after all just a marketing company with a product they want to sell. I'm sure their financial/statistical department is working overtime crunching numbers to figure out how to make money off us without pissing us off enough to quit.<br>
<br>
Then again, I'm just a cynic. <p></p><i></i></td></tr></table> </td></tr></table> <table border=0 width=95%><tr><td align=left valign="top"> </td><td align=right valign="top"><a href="http://pub75.ezboard.com/fwraith27960general.showPrevMessage?topicID=1035.topic"> << Prev Topic</a>&nbsp;| <a href="http://pub75.ezboard.com/fwraith27960general.showNextMessage?topicID=1035.topic"> Next Topic >> </a><br><br><a self href=http://pub75.ezboard.com/fwraith27960general.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=1035.topic&index=0><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/grunge/addReply.jpg border=0 alt="Add Reply"></a> </td></tr></table><br><table width=95% border=0><td valign="top"><a href=http://pub75.ezboard.com/fwraith27960general.threadControl?topicID=1035.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/professional/deleteThread.gif border=0 alt="Topic Control Image"> Topic Commands</a><br> <a href=http://pub75.ezboard.com/fwraith27960general.subscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=1035.topic>Subscribe</a> Click to receive email notification of replies<br>  <a href=http://pub75.ezboard.com/fwraith27960general.unsubscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=1035.topic>Unsubscribe</a> Click to stop receiving email notification of replies<br> </td><td align="right" valign="top"></td></tr><tr align="right"><td colspan=2><form action=http://pub75.ezboard.com/BBSForum.jumpShowForum method=post><table border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="1"><tr><td><b>jump to:</b><select name=forumName><option value="wraith27960general">Tavern<option value="wraith27960frm23">Recruitment Desk<option value="wraith27960frm22">Trading Post<option value="wraith27960frm24">Photo Album<option value="wraith27960wraithmembers">Wraith Members (Old Section)<option value="wraith27960frm20">Wraith Members (New Section)<option value="wraith27960frm21">Recruit Discussion<option value="wraith27960frm29">General / Raids<option value="wraith27960frm27">Points Discussion<option 